<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！” 贾森看到雪莉老师后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师戴着厨师帽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这意味着他们今天要煮东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上关掉游戏，围上围裙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做什么？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一顿为特别的客人准备的特别晚餐。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“客人？” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么客人？” 莉琪问，“他们是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们开始吧。这样才能在他们来的时候准备好。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起一张菜单。“波比，我们今晚要吃什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“番茄酱意大利面。” 波比念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们要做酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森，我们该做什么呢？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森已经读好了说明。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿了一个量杯。“我们用锅加热橄榄油。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，加入切碎的蒜头。” 莉琪念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个大大的蒜头！” 她想象一个大头盯着她看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蒜头不是一个头，是这个。” 贾森拿起一个蒜头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森说得对。” 雪莉老师给莉琪一些切碎的蒜头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“炒三分钟。” 尼娜念道，“我来设闹钟！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在加入番茄。” 波比把两罐番茄倒进锅里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加入辣椒粉。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他撒了一点辣椒粉。“这样酱就会变辣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么会知道这么多？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我喜欢做饭。我还经常帮爸爸妈妈做饭。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用小火煮一个小时。” 尼娜念道，“一个小时？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，需要煮很长时间。这样很好。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我们需要为客人做准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要清理，摆好桌子，还要煮意大利面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁要整理滑板和球？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我！” 波比和贾森同时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁要摆桌子？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们！” 尼娜和莉琪一起说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们清理了东西，也摆好了桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>体育馆看上去像个餐厅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在该煮意大利面了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加一些盐，把水煮沸。” 贾森念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些就够了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水煮沸了！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加入意大利面，煮十一分钟。” 波比念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“桌子看上去很不错。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的客人到底是谁呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师还是没有说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该沥干意大利面了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们把意大利面和酱放到大碗里混合起来。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后等待。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人敲门。“请进！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是爸爸妈妈们！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸、妈妈。” 贾森惊讶地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们就是特别的客人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说你们都是出色的厨师。” 贾森的妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“意大利面闻起来真香。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃起来也一定很香。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们忙了一下午。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师总能找到超级棒的食谱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还告诉我们怎么煮。” 贾森补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这很有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>